  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Create mouthwatering recipes for ultimate customer satisfaction</strong></h2>Experiment and refine your recipes through fun trial and error. Customers' preferences can change at any moment, so stay adaptable!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/eab3d7fb40a1c20e77e60071949a74a0.poster.avif?t=1758380127\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/eab3d7fb40a1c20e77e60071949a74a0.webm?t=1758380127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/eab3d7fb40a1c20e77e60071949a74a0.mp4?t=1758380127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Upgrade your shop and unlock new possibilities</strong></h2>Invest wisely in upgrades and watch your business flourish. More exciting upgrades, like a delivery service, await you as you progress!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/c4750d6a936ef69e1a7de98b292b9c97.poster.avif?t=1758380127\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/c4750d6a936ef69e1a7de98b292b9c97.webm?t=1758380127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/c4750d6a936ef69e1a7de98b292b9c97.mp4?t=1758380127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Efficiently manage your stock and storage</strong></h2>Purchase Boba Tea ingredients from the supermarket and optimize your limited storage space. Stay prepared for future challenges!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/6a01633e6a0da752c6b203df0887c833.poster.avif?t=1758380127\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/6a01633e6a0da752c6b203df0887c833.webm?t=1758380127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/6a01633e6a0da752c6b203df0887c833.mp4?t=1758380127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build a dream team to boost your sales</strong></h2>Recruit talented staff members to enhance your customer experience. Adapt to changing demands and conquer the competition!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/2c138bba48f90ab85fecd659535cab81.poster.avif?t=1758380127\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/2c138bba48f90ab85fecd659535cab81.webm?t=1758380127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/2c138bba48f90ab85fecd659535cab81.mp4?t=1758380127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unlock new branches and explore exciting features</strong></h2>Expand your empire and gain access to game-changing features like the mixer, VIP customers, and sub-branches. Unleash your full potential!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/63d8f143a23d7a26838973d67de8ff4d.poster.avif?t=1758380127\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/63d8f143a23d7a26838973d67de8ff4d.webm?t=1758380127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/63d8f143a23d7a26838973d67de8ff4d.mp4?t=1758380127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
